sql: SELECT iso, adm1, alert__year, alert__week, SUM(alert__count) AS alert__count, confidence__cat  FROM data WHERE iso = '<iso>' AND confidence__cat = 'h' AND ( ((alert__year = 2012 AND alert__week > 38) AND (alert__year = 2012 AND alert__week <= 42)) OR  ((alert__year = 2013 AND alert__week > 38) AND (alert__year = 2013 AND alert__week <= 42)) OR  ((alert__year = 2014 AND alert__week > 38) AND (alert__year = 2014 AND alert__week <= 42)) OR  ((alert__year = 2015 AND alert__week > 38) AND (alert__year = 2015 AND alert__week <= 42)) OR  ((alert__year = 2016 AND alert__week > 37) AND (alert__year = 2016 AND alert__week <= 41)) OR  ((alert__year = 2017 AND alert__week > 38) AND (alert__year = 2017 AND alert__week <= 42)) OR  ((alert__year = 2018 AND alert__week > 38) AND (alert__year = 2018 AND alert__week <= 42)) OR  ((alert__year = 2019 AND alert__week > 38) AND (alert__year = 2019 AND alert__week <= 42)) OR  ((alert__year = 2020 AND alert__week > 38) AND (alert__year = 2020 AND alert__week <= 42))) GROUP BY iso, adm1, alert__year, alert__week
